      • setBriefcase

        private void setBriefcase()
        This method randomly places the briefcase by calling Dice.roll(). It then creates a temporary String[][] that stores the briefcase. Any time a Player enters a room, it checks to see if that room corresponds to the temporary room, holding the case. If so, the player wins and the game ends.
